::DarkMouse::

Quickstrike was holding her.  She gives a deep sigh. "I can't wait 
untiil I'm fighting fit again. But at this rate, the war will be over 
before I can get to the battle field." She turned her head to look at 
Quickstrike. "You can put me down on the table. Please."
She looked at the ground, still shaking a little. The shaking was 
bothering her.  She wondered if she would have to deal with it from 
now on or wold it go away in time. She was also having trouble with 
her beast mode.  She couldn't transform.  She hoped that would return 
to her as well.
